Kenzo gently took Nightlight from Ydrassis's arms.  He turned to Rodimus.
"I'll need to take her to the medical bay for a proper analysis." He
reported.  He carried her to med bay and set her down in a machine
similar to a CR chamber but for more detailed repair.  He punched in
some commands to begin a scan for the problem and awaited the results.
